# local.md (personal override)

This file is the **gitignored personal-config** layer.
Only put items here that should override PROJECT.md. Agents Read this before PROJECT.md.

To use this file, copy `local.md.example` to `local.md`.

---

## Personal working org

(Example)
- Default sandbox alias: `mydev`
- When working against production, always dry-run first.

## Temporary overrides

(Example — trying out a policy under review)
- Temporarily switch the sharing default from `with sharing` to `inherited sharing` (this week's experiment).

## Personal conventions

(Example)
- Debug log prefix: `[mz]` (to be removed before code review).
